1 (c) The Committee, upon the approval of the Medical Board, shall establish fees not
2 exceeding the following amounts:
3 (1) License application $350.00$400.00
4 (2) Biennial renewal of license $350.00$400.00
5 (3) Late renewal of license $100.00
6 (4) Provisional license $175.00$200.00
7 (5) Copies of rules Cost."
8 SECTION 5. The North Carolina Medical Board may adopt temporary rules to
9 implement the provisions of this act.
10 SECTION 6. This act becomes effective October 1, 2025.
